data.name: grdSangByung.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT A.SANG_NAME SANG_NAME FROM OUTSANG A WHERE A.BUNHO = :f_bunho AND :f_order_date BETWEEN A.SANG_START_DATE AND NVL(A.SANG_END_DATE,TO_DATE('2999/01/01','YYYY/MM/DD')) GROUP BY A.SANG_NAME ORDER BY 1
